{"tid":1881494,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"流亡藝術家艾未未：武漢肺炎是「中國製造」裡最響亮的品牌","createTime":"2020-02-15T14:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T15:34:18.000Z","uid":48040,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45e8beb58adfc99f1a329707044efe3be40af409","tid":1881494,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:49:51.000Z","msg":"下一步，要全力以赴地根據&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;的戰略規劃，將這個品牌推廣到全世界。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51485043\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51485043&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFxyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=cf75797b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51485043&h=6432a84d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51485043</a><br />\n<br />\n中國知名藝術家和異見人士艾未未接受BBC時政談話類節目《HARDtalk》專訪，談他流亡他鄉的生活，對中國政治體制的譴責，和對歐洲移民問題的擔憂&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n艾未未認為，英國政府允許華為有限度參與5G網絡建設是目光短淺之舉。他還批評中國政府刻意隱瞞肺炎疫情，造成擴散，使新型冠狀病毒成為「中國製造」裏最響亮的牌子。<br />\n<br />\n艾未未否認自己背叛了國家，但他認為自己有生之年不會回到故土。"},{"pid":"357c07687777e5d20bcd3eaa6fd95865650470d8","tid":1881494,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFxyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=84080eb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"}]}